//Modified by Nintenlord

#include EAstdlib.event

EventPointerTable(0x7,ThisChapter)

ORG StartOffset
ThisChapter:
POIN TurnBasedEvents
POIN CharacterBasedEvents
POIN LocationBasedEvents
POIN MiscBasedEvents
POIN Dunno Dunno Dunno
POIN TrapData TrapData
POIN PlayerUnits
POIN $0 $0 $0 $0 $0 $0
POIN BeginningScene EndingScene

TurnBasedEvents:
END_MAIN
ALIGN 32 //For some reason, CharacterBasedEvents have to be 32-Aligned?

CharacterBasedEvents:
END_MAIN

LocationBasedEvents:

Seize(22,4)

END_MAIN

MiscBasedEvents:
CauseGameOverIfLordDies
END_MAIN

Dunno:
END_MAIN

TrapData:
ENDTRAP

ALIGN 4

PlayerUnits:

 UNIT Roy EirikaLord Roy Level(20,Ally,True) [2,16] 0x0 0x0 0x0 0x1 [Rapier,Vulnerary,Metis'sTome] NoAI

 UNIT Marcus Paladin Roy Level(1,Ally,False) [1,17] 0x0 0x0 0x0 0x1 [SilverLance,SteelSword] NoAI
EnemyUnits:
 
 UNIT Gilliam Armour Knight Gilliam Level(5,Enemy,True) [22,4] 0x0 0x0 0x0 0x1 [SilverLance] NoAI

BeginningScene:

LOAD1 1 PlayerUnits

ENUN

CGText(PrologueStart)


LOAD1 0 EnemyUnits

ENUN

ENDA

EndingScene:
MoveToChapter(NextChapter)
ENDA

MESSAGE Events end at offset CURRENTOFFSET